Note: Java→HIR Translation Tests
Note: ============================================================================

@TestCases:
End-to-end: parses an empty class, runs translate_to_hir, and asserts the
resulting HIR pointer is non-null. Locks down the trivial happy path
through the Java->HIR pipeline.
@End TestCases
Process called "test_java_to_hir_class" returns Integer:
    Note: Test Java to HIR class translation

    Display "Testing Java to HIR class translation..."
    Display ""

    Let source be "public class MyClass { }"
    Let lexer be proc create_java_lexer from Lexer with source
    Let parser be proc create_parser from Parser with lexer

    Let ast be proc parse from Parser with parser
    Let hir be proc translate_to_hir from ToHIR with ast

    Let _hir_ok be hir is not equal to 0
    proc test_assert with _hir_ok, "HIR should not be null"

    Display "PASS: Java to HIR class translation test"
    Display ""

    Return 1
End Process

